Context: The Centre for Community Services & Early Childhood at George Brown College is seeking donations to support students. Donations will go directly towards student scholarships and will be tax deductible. Interested individuals can sign up to receive college news, application deadlines, and event updates by visiting the website or contacting ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The phone number for inquiries is 416-415-2000 with a TTY line at 1-877-515-5559. The college's social media hub can also be visited for more information. It is important to note that the information on the website may be subject to change without notice and students are responsible for verifying fee requirements.
